Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest related

related

Purpose:
  Move from one Wiki Graph object to related objects.

Usage:
  spinedigest related <archive.sdpub> <uri> [--type <entity|triple|source|summary|chunk>] [--chapter <ids>] [--predicate <text>] [--limit <n>] [--cursor <token>] [--json|--jsonl] [--help|-h]

Examples:
  spinedigest related book.sdpub wikigraph://entity/Q162593
  spinedigest related book.sdpub wikigraph://chunk/123 --type source
